{
  "texts": [
    "The maximum number of training epochs was set to 300, with an initial learning rate of 5 e -4, which was decreased to 5 e -5 at the 200th epoch.",
    "At the 240th epoch, the learning rate was further reduced to e -5.",
    "To ensure training stability and efficiency, the minimum batch size was set to 20.",
    "The loss function of the model primarily comprises three constituents: classification loss (L cls), bounding box regression loss (L box), and human keypoint loss (L kpoints).",
    "The changes in the loss functions during model training are illustrated in Fig. 8."
  ]
}